2190 <h3 class="Uo8X3b OhScic zsYMMe">Описание</h3>

2192 <span>Katalon Studio - это программный инструмент для автоматизации тестирования, разработанный Katalon, Inc.</span>

2209 <h3 class="Uo8X3b OhScic zsYMMe">Описание</h3>
2210 <span>Katalon Studio is an automation testing software tool developed by Katalon, Inc. The software is built on top of the open-source automation frameworks Selenium, Appium with a specialized IDE interface for web, API, mobile and desktop application testing. Its initial release for internal use was in January 2015.</span>

2190 <h3 class="Uo8X3b OhScic zsYMMe">Описание</h3>

2192 <span>Katalon Studio - это программный инструмент для автоматизации тестирования, разработанный Katalon, Inc.</span>

2209 <h3 class="Uo8X3b OhScic zsYMMe">Описание</h3>
2210 <span>Katalon Studio is an automation testing software tool developed by Katalon, Inc. The software is built on top of the open-source automation frameworks Selenium, Appium with a specialized IDE interface for web, API, mobile and desktop application testing. Its initial release for internal use was in January 2015.</span>
